entities.description: A comparison chart showing query efficiency with two metrics: Query Time in seconds and Token cost, depicted through bar graphs under the label 'Qasper'.

The dataset or system for which the query efficiency in terms of time and token cost is compared.

The unit in which Token cost is measured, representing millions of tokens on the chart's vertical axis.
